<p><img alt="" src="../Images/2023-02-28T10-39-49-00-00/bfe82cb69fd6b38b3da208aafab5351e-800x445.jpg" /></p>
<p><strong>Gadchiroli District, February 28, 2023:</strong> A squad of Naxalites set ablaze avehicle engaged in road construction work in Maharashtra's Gadchirolidistrict, police said on Tuesday.</p>
<p>According to a police official, at around 11 pm on Monday, armed Naxalitescame to the construction site at Botanpundi-Visamundi road and set afire thevehicle, a mixer truck.</p>
<p>After the incident came to light on Tuesday morning, the Tadgaon policeinspected the spot and registered a case.</p>
